name: Terminal (Unedited Original)
description: Terminal is an homage to a faceless, nameless man who inspired focused strength amidst the chaos. Taken within the five-or-so seconds before the train doors closed and I was shuttled off to my next stop, this photo captures a split moment of independence in a crowded city. I’ve often wondered how much this man did, or didn’t, have to lose. At least, at that precise moment in time.  READ MORE ABOUT THIS PHOTO: Uuyuc.art/kintsugi2016
